com.metreeca.rest

Interface Engine

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GraphEngine

    public interface Engine
    Storage engine.

    Manages storage transactions and performs CRUD actions on LDP resources and containers.

    When operating on containers, engines select the operating profile according to the rdf:type property of the target, as inferred either from metadata annotations or field constraints in the provided shape, defaulting to the Basic profile if no metadata is available:

    See Also:
    Linked Data Platform 1.0

      • engine

      • exec

        <R> R exec(Supplier<R> task)
        Executes a task within a storage transaction.

        If a transaction is not already active on the underlying storage, begins one and commits it on successful task completion; if the task throws an exception, the transaction is rolled back and the exception rethrown; in either case, no action is taken if the transaction was already terminated inside the task.

        Falls back to plain task execution if transactions are not supported by this engine.

        Type Parameters:
        R - the type of the value returned by the task
        Parameters:
        task - the task to be executed
        Returns:
        the value returned by task
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if task is null or returns a null value

      • relate

        Collection<Statement> relate(IRI resource,
                             Query query)
        Relates a resource.
        Parameters:
        resource - the IRI identifying the resource whose description is to be retrieved
        query - the query defining the details of resource to be retrieved;
        Returns:
        the description of resource matched by query; empty if a matching description for resource was not found; related resources matched by query are linked to resource with the ldp:contains property
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if either resource or query is null
        UnsupportedOperationException - if resource retrieval is not supported by this engine
